# Pattern matching on a Scala 3 `enum`

R.2.3 lowers Scala 3 `enum` to Rust `enum` with struct-like variants,
and `match` to Rust `match`.

```scalascript
enum Shape:
  case Circle(r: Double)
  case Square(s: Double)

def area(sh: Shape): Double = sh match
  case Circle(r) => 3.14 * r * r
  case Square(s) => s * s

@main def run(): Unit = println(area(Circle(3.0)))
```

Build and run:

```bash
ssc build-rust shape-match.ssc
./shape-match              # → 28.26
```
